title: Latest news & Browns vs. Bengals preview
itunes:title: Latest news & Browns vs. Bengals preview
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- go over the latest news in the NFL, preview the Thursday Night Football game between the Browns and Bengals. Plus the return of everyone's favorite trivia game "Win Gregg's Toaster"
